    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Textile made from silk fibers produced by wild silk worms. Given that the fibers are usually brown in color, the textile, when dyed, is typically dyed dark colors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
